assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Harbin VITI Electronics Co., Ltd. researches and develops, manufactures, and sells automobile electronic products for cars and buses in China. It offers digital color LCD combination instrument, switch module, slave module, and master module; bridge, processor, and management module, and bus instrument; and bus rear light module, headlight module, chassis module and bus top control module. The company also provides bus signal distribution module, door control module, tire pressure monitoring system, vehicle remote wireless monitoring system, and fuel data acquisition module; combination instrument; vehicle travelling data recorder, and recorder display and printing module; and central processor. In addition, it offers central processor electrical box; retarder power switch; and trunk light control module, retarder control unit, speed control, wiper intermittent controller, flash relay, water level alarm controller, rocker switch lightbox, overvoltage protection controller; retarder foot controller, and engine stall delay relay. Further, the company provides sensor products comprising liquid level alarm switches, capacitive and resistive fuel level sensors, temperature sensors, odometer sensors, speed sensor, air pressure sensors, water level alarms, low air pressure alarms, electronic speed sensors, oil pressure alarm sensors, temperature alarm sensors, magnetic reed oil level sensors, and swing arm oil level sensors. Harbin VITI Electronics Co., Ltd. was founded in 2000 and is based in Harbin, China.
